25-02-19 22:30:33'),(2375,'938','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','The following cases do not correspond to personal information Information on deceased persons, corporations, groups or objects does not correspond to personal information The statistics of the group achieved by gathering together do not correspond to personal information There are no special restrictions on the type, form, nature, and format of information Information that is difficult to identify a specific individual is not personal information \"Easily combined with other information\" means that the possibility of obtaining other information to be combined must be possible &d the possibility of combining with other information must be high','',6,NULL,NULL,'2025-02-19 22:30:33','2025-02-19 22:30:33'),(2376,'939','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'',3,'67b65b9650c5c.png','/storage/tables/67b65b9650c5c.png','2025-02-19 22:30:33','2025-02-19 22:30:46'),(2377,'939','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'',5,'67b65b96667df.png','/storage/tables/67b65b96667df.png','2025-02-19 22:30:33','2025-02-19 22:30:46'),(2378,'939','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','The key terms related to the processing of personal information are as follows.','',1,NULL,NULL,'2025-02-19 22:30:33','2025-02-19 22:30:33'),(2379,'939','App\\Models\\Subsection','Text','The basic matters of personal information protection specified in the Personal Information Protection Act are as follows <Table 100  Basic matters of personal information protection','',4,NULL,NULL,'2025-02-19 22:30:33','2025-02-19 22:30:33'),(2380,'940','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'',5,'67b65b968b4b8.png','/storage/tables/67b65b968b4b8.png','2025-02-19 22:30:33','2025-02-19 22:30:46'),(2381,'940','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'',8,'67b65b96acbfc.png','/storage/tables/67b65b96acbfc.png','2025-02-19 22:30:33','2025-02-19 22:30:46'),(2382,'940','App\\Models\\Subsection','Tables',NULL,'',9,'67b65b96c54b3.png','/storage/tables/67b65b96c54b3.png',