18:28'),(2889,1,'Test','How would you describe the function of a queue in data processing? A queue allows data to be processed in a first-in-first-out manner, facilitating orderly handling of tasks.',0.4,-1.8,'Easy','C1-5plFkAgqSF6toAeyOTR18A','Multiple Choice - Single','\"Facilitating orderly handling of tasks.\"','[\"Allowing random access to data.\", \"Facilitating orderly handling of tasks.\", \"Storing data in a hierarchical manner.\", \"Processing data in a last-in-first-out manner.\"]','2025-03-24 06:18:28','2025-03-24 06:18:28'),(2890,1,'Test','What is a key characteristic of a tree data structure? A tree expands from a root node and has a hierarchical relationship among its elements.',0.6,0.2,'Average','C1-aImVQVwsQ4GAszg1ykr+wQ','Multiple Choice - Single','\"It has a hierarchical relationship.\"','[\"It has a linear relationship.\", \"It has a hierarchical relationship.\", \"It is always balanced.\", \"It has a fixed number of nodes.\"]','2025-03-24 06:18:28','2025-03-24 06:18:28'),(2891,1,'Test','When analyzing algorithms, what does time complexity refer to? Time complexity measures the time required for an algorithm to execute based on the number of operations performed.',0.6,-0.4,'Average','C1-XocTRupLRrGSMTzQ3cjROA','Multiple Choice - Single','\"The time required for an algorithm to execute.\"','[\"The space required for an algorithm to execute.\", \"The time required for an algorithm to execute.\", \"The number of lines of code.\", \"The complexity of the data structure used.\"]','2025-03-24 06:18:28','2025-03-24 06:18:28'),(2892,1,'Test','Which data structures are best suited for implementing a stack? A stack can be implemented using arrays or linked lists, allowing for efficient data management.',0.6,0,'Average','C1-pUWaTT9aQ5W4PWSWYlK20A','Multiple Choice - Many','[\"Arrays\", \"Linked Lists\"]','[\"Arrays\", \"Trees\", \"Graphs\", \"Linked Lists\"]','2025-03-24 06:18:28','2025-03-24 06:18:28'),(2893,1,'Test','What are the key factors to consider w