ect focused on big data analysis. Considering the strengths and weaknesses of both types of languages, which would you recommend for this project and why? Provide a detailed rationale based on the context.',1,4,'Very Hard','C1-RRhb6ypgTD6soxdmc4zexQ','Multiple Choice - Single','\"Python language\"','[\"Python language\", \"C language\", \"Java language\", \"JavaScript language\"]','2025-03-24 06:18:28','2025-03-24 06:18:28'),(2904,1,'Test','An IT team is assessing the need for an Integrated Development Environment (IDE) for their new software project. What two key benefits should they consider when evaluating IDEs, based on the characteristics of IDEs mentioned in the context? Justify your selections with relevant details.',1,3.6,'Very Hard','C1-czEU2SjMRIugTJjrsNqVig','Multiple Choice - Many','[\"Bundled functions for coding and debugging\", \"Interactive interface for ease of use\"]','[\"Bundled functions for coding and debugging\", \"Requires separate tools for different tasks\", \"Interactive interface for ease of use\", \"Limited support for programming languages\"]','2025-03-24 06:18:28','2025-03-24 06:18:28');
